data.description: !!BACK ON MARKET DUE TO BUYER FINANCING!!Don't miss out on this spacious 3 bedroom 1 bath Cape Cod. located on the east end of Springfield. This move in ready home features 2 lower bedrooms and a 3rd large upstairs bedroom. Enjoy the private back yard with tons of mature landscaping and privacy fence. Featuring a large 12*20 family room off of the kitchen with access to the garage. Fresh paint throughout and all new vinyl flooring. Fully updated bathroom and kitchen. Loads of storage space and a partially finished basement with a laundry room. Large corner lot with off street parking.  Schedule your private showing today!
